{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create another section with id="book-services" using the same colours, rounded cards, padding and overall style as the previous section and tentree.com. Add an H2: “Book Professional Printing Services by Technology” and a short paragraph about UV, eco and latex printing done in-house in Noida. Add 3 pill-style tabs: UV Printing, Eco Printing, Latex Printing. Each tab should show service cards styled like the product cards: rounded white card with soft shadow, service image on top, service title as H3, short description, and a full-width pill “Book Service” button linking to a page picker. Use horizontal scroll on mobile and a neat grid on desktop.
{% enddoc %}
